#FBF My summer so far…

Such great memories include a beautiful dinner arranged by my dear friends, Dayssi and Paul; a lovely Farfetch x Altuzarra soirée on Shelter Island with @Jannabullock; hosting Audrey’s Gruss’ birthday luncheon with @Amy_hoadley; @TODS exhibition celebration of A MOMENT IN TIME: Iconic Images by Harry Benson; TOD’S Summer Celebration with Erica Reid featuring @Saltnpepaofficial; Alvin Bragg’s campaign reception; hosting a luncheon alongside Janna celebrating @Micheleokadoner ’s presentation at the @Longhousereserve and her new book A SEED TAKES ROOT; an evening full of dancing at The Bridgehampton Childcare and Community Center’s Jazz Soul Celebration with @tamronhall; THE BODY: The Watermill Center Summer Benefit featuring a roster of groundbreaking international artists to bring a series of installations and performances across the Watermill Center’s property; lunch with the fabulous @Countessluann at @Toppingrosehouse; the Southampton Hospital’s 65th Annual Summer Party honoring Audrey and Martin Gruss and John Paulson; the HDRF Race of Hope with @Lauranicklasnyc @Anna.zaoui and @CarolynSchenk12; an afternoon spent on Sunset Beach; seeing @ReneeCox’s show A PROOF OF BEING at @Guild_hall with the artist herself and @Khatch1234; @Mmfineartgallery ’s exhibition SERENITY presenting @Christophevonhohenberg ’s black-and-white photographs of the Hamptons against the blazing summer sun and @Strongcuevas ’s sculptures that explore recurring themes of outer space exploration and inner consciousness; lastly, it was so great to see @humaabedin at the Métier dinner hosted by Sara Byworth @thumps1979 and @Melissa.metier - I loved sitting across from deneebenton.

